  "description": "Kazokucon is a small Oslo-based pop-culture and cosplay convention with a strong community-first ethos — the name plays on the Japanese word for \"family\". Programming spans anime, manga, fantasy, sci-fi, comics, video games, tabletop, cosplay and K-pop, with an emphasis on a cozy, welcoming atmosphere over scale.\n\nEditions are themed; the upcoming 2026 edition is branded \"Neon Age\".",
